This paper represents the state of the art of the industry and its technological advances in the fields of industry, predictive maintenance and visual indicators. The methodology of this study will be described. The most relevant articles are mentioned along with their use and application. Mixed reality is the key tool for intelligent industry. The use of artificial intelligence in maintenance through machine learning is becoming necessary to meet new challenges. The combination of predictive maintenance and mixed reality holds great promise for improving plant efficiency and reliability. It will enable operators to make more informed decisions to avoid production shutdowns.